{"word":"ἐπιχράω 2","slug":"ἐπιχράω 2","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n41660\" key=\"e)pixra/w2\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐπιχράω</orth> (B), (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χράω</foreign> B), poet. word, only <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">aor. 2</tns> or <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπέχρᾰον,</foreign> <sense id=\"n41660.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">attack, assault,</tr_> c. dat., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὡς δὲ λύκοι ἄρνεσσιν ἐπέχραον..ὣς Δαναοὶ Τρώεσσιν ἐπέχραον,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:352\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.352</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:356\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">356</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μητέρι μοι μνηστῆρες ἐπέχραον</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">beset</tr_> her, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:50\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.50</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n41660.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> abs., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be violent, rage,</tr_> of the winds, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:498\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.498</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n41660.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be urgent</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">eager</tr_> to do, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:508\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.508</biblScope> </bibl> : c. acc. et <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνάγκη</foreign>] <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">με..νεῖσθαι ἐπέχραε</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">was urgent</tr_> that I should come, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:431\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.431</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}